---
description: Settings/profile workspace contract, including elevated controls.
globs:
  - "app/profile/**/*.tsx"
  - "components/profile/**/*.tsx"
  - "components/settings/**/*.tsx"
  - "app/styles/settings.css"
  - "app/styles/forms.css"
alwaysApply: true
---

The profile/settings workspace must stay aligned with `AGENTS.md`.

Key rules:
- `Additional filters` and `Experience tabs` share one elevated-control contract.
- Keep profile/settings cleanup zero-diff unless the request explicitly changes the layout.
- Text fields are transparent with bottom-border treatment unless a listed exception already exists.
- Keep upload, disclosure, and footer spacing consistent with the current settings surface.
- Do not invent new settings layout patterns when the existing section/disclosure structure already covers the need.
